This project is a simple real estate application that allows users to register as buyers or sellers, post properties for sale, and express interest in properties. The application includes user authentication, property management, and email notifications for interest tracking.



Install dependencies:

npm install
Create a .env file in the root directory with the following 

contents:

MONGO_URI=your_mongo_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
EMAIL=your_email@example.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your_email_password

Start the server:

npm start

Access the application:
Open your browser and navigate to http://localhost:5000.